      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Steffan Westcott</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/steffanwestcott/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/c/c4/Steffan-westcott.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Steffan-westcott.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Steffan Westcott <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Steffan Westcott</b>,<br />\nan English senior software engineer affiliated with the travel management company <i>Click Travel Ltd</i>. <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>,\nfocusing on frameworks for <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Enterprise_software\">enterprise applications</a> on <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amazon_Web_Services\">Amazon Web Services</a> (AWS) using <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Domain-driven_design\">domain-driven design</a> (DDD) <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\nHe holds a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bachelor_of_Arts\">BA</a> degree in mathematics and computation from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Keble_College,_Oxford\">Keble College, Oxford</a> in 1993,\nand brought many innovations into chess programming concerning <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">bitboards</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Innovations\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Innovations</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Innovations\">Innovations</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steffan_Westcott&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Innovations\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/All_Shortest_Paths\" title=\"All Shortest Paths\">All Shortest Paths</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/King_Pattern#FloodFillAlgorithms\" title=\"King Pattern\">Flood Fill Algorithms</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Kogge-Stone_Algorithm\" title=\"Kogge-Stone Algorithm\">Kogge-Stone Algorithm</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Parallel_Prefix_Algorithms\" title=\"Parallel Prefix Algorithms\">Parallel Prefix Algorithms</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steffan_Westcott&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Design_Principles\" title=\"Design Principles\">Design Principles</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steffan_Westcott&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steffan_Westcott&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=251180\">Re: algorithm question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steffan Westcott</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 09, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/King_Pattern#FloodFillAlgorithms\" title=\"King Pattern\">Flood Fill Algorithms</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=252020\">All shortest paths &amp; other flood-fill based algorithms</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steffan Westcott</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 13, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/All_Shortest_Paths\" title=\"All Shortest Paths\">All Shortest Paths</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=252289\">Re: flood fill attack bitboards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steffan Westcott</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 15, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Kogge-Stone_Algorithm\" title=\"Kogge-Stone Algorithm\">Kogge-Stone Algorithm</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=261259\">Bitboard algorithm design principles</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steffan Westcott</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 23, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Design_Principles\" title=\"Design Principles\">Design Principles</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=266275\">Re: significant math</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steffan Westcott</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 20, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=266282\">Re: significant math</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steffan Westcott</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 20, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=398361\">Re: Bitboards, pre-computing moves, and blocked squares?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steffan Westcott</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 30, 2004</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steffan_Westcott&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=490129\">Re: algorithm question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steffan Westcott</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 27, 2006&#160;» <a href=\"/Traversing_Subsets_of_a_Set\" title=\"Traversing Subsets of a Set\">Traversing Subsets of a Set</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=491079\">Re: Some thoughts on Dann Corbit's rotated alternative</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steffan Westcott</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 03, 2006&#160;» <a href=\"/Occupancy_of_any_Line\" title=\"Occupancy of any Line\">Occupancy of any Line</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=26152&amp;start=13\">Re: Zobrist key random numbers</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steffan Westcott</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 22, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Zobrist_Hashing\" title=\"Zobrist Hashing\">Zobrist Hashing</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=28545&amp;start=2\">Re: On Zobrist keys</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steffan Westcott</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 22, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Zobrist_Hashing\" title=\"Zobrist Hashing\">Zobrist Hashing</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steffan_Westcott&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=38478&amp;start=8\">Re: Possible Board Presentation and Move Generation for GPUs</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steffan Westcott</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 20, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/GPU\" title=\"GPU\">GPU</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steffan_Westcott&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/steffanwestcott/\">Steffan Westcott | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://plus.google.com/108745504931571194860\">Steffan Westcott - Google+</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/clicktravel-steffan\">clicktravel-steffan (Steffan Westcott)· GitHub</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steffan_Westcott&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/steffanwestcott/\">Steffan Westcott | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://gk.news/clicktravel/press-release/click-travel-takes-top-tech-accolade-silicon-canal-awards/attachment/011-click-travel-named-large-tech-company-of-the-year/\">Click-Travel-named-Large-Tech-Company-of-the-Year - Click Travel</a>, November 30, 2017</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\